Complete Mitogenomes of Polypedates Tree Frogs Unveil Gene Rearrangement and 
Concerted Evolution within Rhacophoridae.

Cui L(1)(2), Huang A(1)(2), He Z(1)(2), Ao L(1)(2), Ge F(1)(2), Fan X(1)(2), 
Zeng B(1)(2), Yang M(1)(2), Yang D(1)(2), Ni Q(1)(2), Li Y(1)(2), Yao Y(3), Xu 
H(3), Yang J(1)(2), Wei Z(4), Li T(5), Yan T(1)(2), Zhang M(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Key Laboratory of Livestock and Poultry Multi-omics, Ministry of Agriculture 
and Rural Affairs, College of Animal Science and Technology, Sichuan 
Agricultural University, Chengdu 611130, China.
(2)Farm Animal Genetic Resources Exploration and Innovation Key Laboratory of 
