Recombinant Expression of Archaeal Superoxide Dismutases in Plant Cell Cultures: 
A Sustainable Solution with Potential Application in the Food Industry.

Gogliettino M(1), Arciello S(2), Cillo F(3), Carluccio AV(3), Palmieri G(1), 
