New Properties of a Well-Known Antioxidant: Pleiotropic Effects of Human 
Lactoferrin in Mice Exposed to Gamma Irradiation in a Sublethal Dose.

Kopaeva MY(1), Alchinova IB(2), Cherepov AB(1), Demorzhi MS(2), Nesterenko 
MV(3), Zarayskaya IY(1), Karganov MY(2).

Author information:
(1)National Research Center "Kurchatov Institute", 1 Akademika Kurchatova Sq., 
